'''氮化锌'''是一种无机化合物，化学式为Zn<sub>3</sub>N<sub>2</sub>。纯的氮化锌的结构属于立方晶系。<ref name="sangeeta">{{cite book | last = Sangeeta | first = D. | title = Inorganic Materials Chemistry Desk Reference | url = http://books.google.com/?id=bdGXyilNsGMC&pg=PA278&dq=%22Zinc+nitride%22 | accessdate = 2007-09-30 | year = 1997 | publisher = [[CRC_Press|CRC Press]] | isbn= 978-0-8493-8900-9 | page = 278}}</ref><ref name="partin">{{cite journal | author = Partin, D. E.; Williams, D. J.; O'Keeffe, M. | year = 1997 | title = The Crystal Structures of Mg<sub>3</sub>N<sub>2</sub> and Zn<sub>3</sub>N<sub>2</sub> | journal = Journal of Solid State Chemistry | volume = 132 | issue = 1 | pages = 56–59 | doi = 10.1006/jssc.1997.7407 | url = http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/els/00224596/1997/00000132/00000001/art97407 | bibcode = 1997JSSCh.132...56P | access-date = 2014-07-12 | archive-date = 2012-10-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121004163119/http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/els/00224596/1997/00000132/00000001/art97407 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==制备==
氮化锌可以通过[[氨基锌|氨基锌]]的在无氧环境中的热分解（200℃）得到，<ref name="roscoe">{{cite book | authorlink1 = Henry Enfield Roscoe | author1 = Roscoe, H. E. | authorlink2 = Carl Schorlemmer | author2 = Schorlemmer, C. | origyear = 1878 | title = A Treatise on Chemistry: Volume II, The Metals | url = http://books.google.com/?id=-K0EAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA650&dq | accessdate = 2007-11-01 | edition = 4th | year = 1907 | publisher  = [[Macmillan_Publishers|Macmillan]] | location = London | pages = 650–651 }}</ref>此反应的副产品是[[氨|氨]]气。<ref name="bloxam">{{cite book | last = Bloxam | first = C. L. | title = Chemistry, Inorganic and Organic | url = http://books.google.com/?id=f9StqQ8YBtwC&pg=PA380 | accessdate = 2007-10-31 | edition = 9th | year = 1903 | publisher = P. Blakiston's Son & Co. | location  = Philadelphia | page = 380 }}</ref>
<blockquote>3Zn(NH<sub>2</sub>)<sub>2</sub> → Zn<sub>3</sub>N<sub>2</sub> + 4[[氨|NH<sub>3</sub>]]</blockquote>

氮化锌也可以在600℃用[[锌|锌]]粉和[[氨|氨]]反应得到，反应会产生氢气：<ref name="roscoe"/><ref>
{{cite book | last = Lowry | first = M. T. | authorlink = Thomas Martin Lowry | title = Inorganic Chemistry | url = http://books.google.com/?id=umQ6AAAAMAAJ&dq=%22zinc+nitride%22&q=%22zinc+nitride%22 | accessdate = 2007-11-01 | year = 1922 | publisher = [[Macmillan_Publishers|Macmillan]] | page = 872 }}</ref>
<blockquote>3[[锌|Zn]] + 2[[氨气|NH<sub>3</sub>]] → Zn<sub>3</sub>N<sub>2</sub> + 3[[氢|H<sub>2</sub>]]</blockquote>
但在实际反应中，会有锌挥发而损失掉。<ref>《无机化合物制备手册》.朱文祥 主编.化学工业出版社. P<sub>379</sub>. 【XII-7】氮化锌（zinc nitride）</ref>

==化学性质==
氮化锌和[[水|水]]剧烈反应，生成氨和[[氧化锌|氧化锌]]：<ref name="roscoe"/><ref name="bloxam"/>
<blockquote>Zn<sub>3</sub>N<sub>2</sub> + 3H<sub>2</sub>O → 3ZnO + 2NH<sub>3</sub></blockquote>
有资料<ref name=wjhxcs>《无机化学丛书》.第六卷 卤素 铜分族 锌分族. 科学出版社. P<sub>544</sub>. (1)氮化锌</ref>则说“氮化锌可以缓慢水解，生成[[氢氧化锌|氢氧化锌]]和氨。”

氮化锌可溶于[[盐酸|盐酸]]。<ref>
{{cite book | author = Comey, A. M.; Hahn, D. A. | title = A Dictionary of Chemical Solubilities: Inorganic | url = http://books.google.com/?id=7L0MAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA1124 | accessdate = 2007-11-01 | edition = 2nd | year = 1921 | publisher  = [[Macmillan_Publishers|Macmillan]] | location = New York | page = 1124 }}</ref> 也可以可逆地和金属[[锂|锂]]发生[[电化学|电化学]]反应。<ref>{{cite book | author = Amatucci, G. G.; Pereira, N. | editor = Nazri, G.-A.; Pistoia, G. | title = Lithium Batteries: Science and Technology | url = http://books.google.com/?id=k4duxuea3eIC&pg=PA256 | accessdate = 2007-11-01 | year = 2004 | publisher = [[Kluwer_Academic_Publishers|Kluwer Academic Publishers]] | isbn = 978-1-4020-7628-2 | chapter = Nitride and Silicide Negative Electrodes | page = 256 }}</ref>

氮化锌在空气中加热即被氧化。和氢在400℃以上反应，得到[[锌|锌]]和[[氨|氨]]。<ref name=wjhxcs />另外，它和[[氮化镁|氮化镁]](Mg<sub>3</sub>N<sub>2</sub>)与[[氮化锂|氮化锂]](Li<sub>3</sub>N)相似，它的[[熔点|熔点]]很高。<ref>{{cite book | author = Grolier Incorporated | title = Academic American Encyclopedia | url = http://books.google.com/?id=YgI4E7w5JI8C&dq=%22zinc+nitride%22&q=%22zinc+nitride%22 | accessdate = 2007-11-01 | year = 1994 | publisher = Grolier Inc. | location = Danbury, CT | isbn = 978-0-7172-2053-3 | page = 202 | archive-date = 2020-03-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200312090742/https://books.google.com/books?id=YgI4E7w5JI8C&dq=%22zinc+nitride%22&q=%22zinc+nitride%22&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>

